Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}「水银灯」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  快点起来  已经7点13分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你还没搞清楚自己的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛…真红最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要  不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要每天早上  都这样吵闹不休！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早的  不要大呼小叫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要听你说教呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  管教仆从  是很重要的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓  你听好  身为仆从的你只能到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「呜」  应该回答「是」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  要去吃早餐了  用这个把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脚超出这条线了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「啊」  你以为这是谁的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房间！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间全部都是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都自己擅自决定  你以为你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这些仆从无论哪个都那么罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还愣在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快点把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  门帮你打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要那么顾虑她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小家伙真是让人觉得火大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  快点吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是为了  真红与雏莓做的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我煎的荷包蛋很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪  你怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  雏莓  你怎么了？你不想吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏喜欢吃白白软软  甜甜的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？白白软软的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是优格对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你还蛮挑食的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是软软的  黑色的  红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色？红色？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  海苔寿司卷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  真红  你知道雏莓喜欢吃什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  这种任性的仆从  我才不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓  画给我看好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真珠夫人的今日运势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  已经到了真珠夫人的时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  我得去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起哦  小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我放学回来  我一定会给你喜欢吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:11.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿大家有美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不去上学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴总是去学校上学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪也去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我是不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有必要去那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直待在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和小雏一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说小雏一个人的时候  不可以从那个皮箱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直待在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管  去哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才讨厌小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么  居然开着没关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的  黑色的  软软的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的  黑色的  软软的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明太子花枝墨汁意大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这道菜不错哦  樱田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  来  要不要喝杯茶啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  我知道新犯人是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  到底是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实犯人就是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么证据说我是犯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件豹纹内裤就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是被害者留下的死亡讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊？  库库侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道的话  拿字典查「海豹」这个词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我的不在场证明  明明做得天衣无缝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再狡辩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:35.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经无法逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶居然在看人偶剧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  安静就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是纯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像不像？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有点像…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我怎么欣赏起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  好脏哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个仆从很吵耶  给我安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  她是你的仆从吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾她是你的工作不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挡住我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  打开电视
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先听我把话说完…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个很甜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏喜欢这个  好想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白的  甜甜的  软软的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的  红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白的  甜甜的  软软的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画的这么难看谁看得懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把地板的涂鸦擦干净哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏真的是孤零零一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人了解小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  巴很了解小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏什么都不用说  她就会买来给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你回到她身边去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我也比较清闲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏也想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏好想回巴的身边去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我们不能在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为巴已经没有戒指了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有戒指的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法从媒介那里  获得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在雏莓能够这样活动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我把从你那里  得到的力量分给了她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓已经无法从你我身边离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是最讨厌小家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭成那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样  只是因为这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直待在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事吗？兔兔夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔兔夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库库侦探  我们破门而入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  不在家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然没得到我的允许  就随便乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  这是什么房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就让我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在这个家里  算是很漂亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  这是厕所！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真红…你不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仆从对主人讲话  居然那么没大没小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不开吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  刚好卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天可以的话  我先帮你留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎再来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也没有的话… 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好去那家店买吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…真红…好重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以说淑女很重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…不行了～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真红  小雏也要去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  你要留在里面看家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？好过份哦  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小雏也要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  是真红吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上帮你开门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓  不要离开我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闹了  你快现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓  到我后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,586920个小时又37分不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你也醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我明明通知过你了  难道你没察觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人偶是你操控的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是跟你打个招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是  为什么游戏的输家会在这里呢？雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败的人偶要把「蔷薇圣母」交给获胜的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为她的粮食才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是爱丽丝游戏的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们玷污了神圣的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多管闲事  我有我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使父亲大人生气也无所谓？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不满的话  我现在可以接受你的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生气的表情  还是一样很难看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西是打不倒我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不玩了～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于愚蠢的家伙要慢慢地折磨才有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的！小心点！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:56.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:57.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:58.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱呢  下次带来给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  带来给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走走走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  还是去游戏厅玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没钱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去你家玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:12.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小野田与伊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我不该出门的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这样空手回去的话  像个白痴似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱田同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然知道那孩子喜欢吃的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:18:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为那个人偶…是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是突然来我家的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天  有一个电话打进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这里是柏叶家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要转吗？还是不转？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾经想趁她睡觉的时候  把她拿去扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  与雏莓在一起生活后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪在她的身边  我明白了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子真的很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人偶究竟是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里来的？究竟想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  有一点我很确定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们非常需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫真红的人偶  还有雏莓都很需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说  雏莓去你那里的时候  我非常担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  现在稍微放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓就拜托你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪里去了？  发生了很严重的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很严重的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真红与水银…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  你看  雏莓你看  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  纯你怎么穿成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～  这个就是软软的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦～  原来是莓大福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软软的  甜甜的  好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我买的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有说要喝红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏现在很喜欢纯  所以要给纯谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢纯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:50.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快从我身上下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  红茶时间到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不及格  重新给我泡一壶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…明明根本还没喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用喝也知道  你泡茶的工夫还有待加强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家很努力练习过的…虽说是在梦里…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全冷掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那孩子在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在你的梦里  她也会教你泡红茶的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梦里？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  蔷薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这只蔷薇戒指发誓吧
